  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA45">
<l>pirāṉavaṉai nōkkum peruneṟiyē pēṇip</l>
<l>pirāṉavaṉṟaṉ pēraruḷē vēṇṭip - pirāṉavaṉai</l>
<l>yeṅkuṟṟā ṉeṉpīrka ḷeṉpōlvār cintaiyiṉu</l>
<l>miṅkuṟṟāṉ kāṇpārk keḷitu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Cherishing the great path that looks upon him as the lord,</l>
<l>desiring the great grace of him who is the lord, of him who is the lord</l>
<l>you say “where does he abide?” More than in the minds of my like</l>
<l>he abides here, easy for those who see him.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
